name: Feed 'em... Till Death
description:
Feed em is about a character stuck in a city filled with greed and consumerism. Trying to survive, our character needs to feed Greeders to get away from them. Collecting coins and using them in order to find food, game get harder and harder since Greeders keep crowding the city and wanting more and more...
